citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:40 am to
12:10pm on 14 April 2021. No response received within 30 minutes to a voicemail left at the listed number and multiple
honks from the driveway. Spoke to neighbor who did not think the licensee was home.
Additional Inspectors:
KATHRYN CAMPITELLI, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICER
Kendra Nicholas, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
